# User management

Changing password age
```
$ chage -m 1 -M 28 -W5 -I 3 -E 2021-12-31 user1
```

Options
```
m -> minimum days user can change passwd again
M -> how many days user must change the passwd
W -> warning before expire the passwd 
I -> Inactivite days, how many days user can login and change passwd after expiring
E -> acct expired
```

Check the man page for help
```
$ man 5 shadow
```

To change password age - easier way
$ chage -l user1

